OL,3,CMusic festival cancelled after 12
OL,4,Cyears due to 'rising costs'
OL,6,FOrganisers of Hardwick Festival in
OL,7,FCounty Durham have confirmed that it
OL,8,Fhas been cancelled for 2026.
OL,10,FThe music festival, which was held in
OL,11,FHardwick Park in Sedgefield, had been
OL,12,Frunning for 12 years with names like
OL,13,FNoel Gallagher, Nile Rodgers, and
OL,14,FStereophonics as previous headliners.
OL,16,FIn a statement released today (7
OL,17,FNovember), the team behind the event
OL,18,Fsaid the impact of rising costs means
OL,19,Fit is "time to hit pause, just for
OL,20,Fnow".
