OL,6,FIt is not the first North East event
OL,7,Fto be affected by financial pressures
OL,8,Fthis year, with Durham Lumiere
OL,9,Fannouncing last month that this
OL,10,Fmonth's edition would be its last
OL,11,Fafter 15 years.
OL,13,FHardwick Festival started out as a one-
OL,14,Fday event in 2013 and was originally
OL,15,Fnamed Hardwick Live. Over the years,
OL,16,Fit grew to a three-day event
OL,17,Fattracting more than 30,000 people
OL,18,Feach August.
