OL,3,CMusic festival cancelled after 12
OL,4,Cyears due to 'rising costs'
OL,6,FA statement released from the festival
OL,7,Fteam reads: "Hardwick Festival has
OL,8,Fbeen an incredible journey. We've
OL,9,Fdanced in the rain, sung our hearts
OL,10,Fout in the sun, and watched our fields
OL,11,Fcome alive with the shared love of
OL,12,Flive music.
OL,14,F"Like many independent festivals,
OL,15,Fwe've felt the growing impact of
OL,16,Frising costs, from infrastructure and
OL,17,Flogistics to artist fees, and despite
OL,18,Four very best efforts, we're unable to
OL,19,Fbring everything together for 2026.
