OL,6,F"We know that times have been hard
OL,7,Fover the last few years and it's been
OL,8,Ftough for us to get ticket sales where
OL,9,Fthey need to be, unfortunately the
OL,10,Fsales haven't matched our ambitions.
OL,12,F"But this isn't goodbye. It's a see
OL,13,Fyou later."
OL,15,FThe organisers added that they'd be
OL,16,Ftaking the time away to "regroup,
OL,17,Freflect, and reimagine" the future of
OL,18,Fthe festival, and "be back when the
OL,19,Ftime is right".
